29:13.099 --> 29:14.459
That's where rib bone is.

29:14.467 --> 29:15.934
Great.

29:15.935 --> 29:17.905
We kill two birds, one stone.
You in?

29:17.906 --> 29:20.733
I was gonna ask you
the same thing.

29:20.740 --> 29:22.740
Go.

29:28.447 --> 29:32.383
Just 'cause my cpu
is far superior to your brain

29:32.384 --> 29:34.814
doesn't mean
I don't understand you.

29:35.987 --> 29:38.790
You were free.

29:38.791 --> 29:42.360
You never had to see me
ever again.

29:42.361 --> 29:44.161
And yet, you couldn't
help yourself.

29:44.163 --> 29:46.431
You had to be...

29:46.432 --> 29:49.502
