straight from the tree.

30:52.131 --> 30:53.831
Oh, shit!

30:53.833 --> 30:55.863
Exactly.

31:05.307 --> 31:07.247
You guys go for the records.

31:07.248 --> 31:10.342
I'll take care of rib bone.

31:10.345 --> 31:11.345
Hey.

31:11.346 --> 31:12.780
Where is he...

31:12.781 --> 31:13.781
sic 'em.

31:15.851 --> 31:19.181
What's your story?

31:19.187 --> 31:21.187
I want my candy.

31:24.859 --> 31:27.759
- Where's my candy?
- Bitch!

31:37.672 --> 31:39.372
Welcome to wonderland, Alice.

31:39.374 --> 31:41.614
<i>Let go of me,
