long-term consequences might be.

32:12.207 --> 32:14.207
She may very well
have permanent psychosis.

32:14.209 --> 32:16.169
She's gonna have to stay
indefinitely.

32:16.178 --> 32:18.178
The state will cover
two weeks payment.

32:18.180 --> 32:21.910
