to pay her bills after that?

32:21.917 --> 32:25.252
I'll figure something out.

32:25.253 --> 32:27.383
Grace!

32:27.389 --> 32:30.819
Wait, Grace! Grace!

32:30.825 --> 32:32.593
Grace!

32:32.594 --> 32:34.594
<i>Grace, don't leave me!</i>

32:34.596 --> 32:37.596
<i>Please, Grace, don't leave me!</i>

32:56.250 --> 32:57.710
Mahalo.

32:59.353 --> 33:00.783
Looking for this?

33:00.789 --> 33:02.689
Fuck did you do to my car?

33:02.691 --> 33:03.891
Who the hell are you?

33:03.892 --> 33:05.962
Try "thank you," it's easier.

33:07.761 --> 33:09.230
I wasn't even in there
for an hour.

33:09.231 --> 33:10.431
How did you do this?

33:10.432 --> 33:13.432
I saw you talking to the primo.

33:13.435 --> 33:15.970
You're a real firecracker.

33:15.971 --> 33:17.771
